file_content.text: Okay, that should take care of Zee's encryption programs. Transmitter's in place. Let me slice into Eidolon's network....
Wow, this is tough. Anuli wasn't kidding. The Eidolon's HoloNet guys know their stuff.
It's professional, that's for sure. Lucky we're better.
It is a security corp.
Looks like their clients were getting their money's worth.
Don't worry, I'll tell your boyfriend how impressive you were.
Showing off for that boy?
I told you he's not my boyfriend. Keep that up and I'm gonna think you're jealous.
Who? Anuli? He's not my boyfriend! We just grew up together. He's more like... my little brother.
Are you finished yet?
Hurry.
Let me concentrate already.
Come on, come on... I'm in! I'll contact Anuli.
Anuli, you getting this? That's quite a data stream, huh?
Beautiful! All Zee's work. A symphony of math. Downloading the files onto the HoloNet now. Stand by.
Let's get outta here before more of the Eidolon's mercs show up. They're way too good with those blasters.
Zee was right. You must be insane--otherwise, why would you be here?
I'm disappointed.
He talked.
Zee knew there was nowhere he could go where "he" wouldn't find him. There's no escaping "him."
You going to keep talking or are we going to do this?
Shut up. Really.
You think too highly of your assassin boss.
Doubtful.
That's because we know him. You clearly have no idea who you're dealing with, you ignorant merc.
I'll leave your body as a calling card.
I don't plan on escaping.
Never trust a Bith.
I'm getting soft.
Zee was a valuable asset. You'll pay for making us kill him.
Stupid to waste resources like that.
Seems pointless.
Learn this, bounty hunter scum--you cross Eidolon Security, you die.
Hang on, I think I got some change somewhere....
Will one credit do?
Let's just do this.
You have very little time to talk. Don't spend it posturing.
Yeah, and?
Who put you up to this? Was it the Cartel?
Professionals don't divulge contacts. You understand.
I'll never tell.
Doesn't matter. We'll get the intel one way or another.
What if it was?
Maybe.
Looks like it's time to eliminate more Hutts. Good. I hate Hutts.
There was nothing else interesting happening on this dull moon.
Nah, I was just bored.
Crazy, worthless hunter.
Eliminate the threat! Now!
